cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.DM

Reasoning problems are often related to artificial intelligence, hence cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with problems related to logic, which suggests cs.LO as another likely sub-category. The use of fixed-parameter tractable reductions and the focus on structural aspects of problem instances suggests cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) and cs.CC (computational complexity) as possible sub-categories. Finally, the paper also mentions combinatorics, which suggests cs.DM (discrete mathematics) as a possible sub-category.
